	var result = '';
	var mark = parseInt(current.getValue('u_mark'));
	var first_mark = parseInt(current.getValue('u_first_mark'));
	if (mark>first_mark){
		result = 'Better';
	}
	else if(mark<first_mark){
		result = 'Worse';
	}
	else{
		result = 'Same';
	}
	g_scratchpad.result = result;
